        "sections": [
            {
                "name": "Ancient Intellects",
                "type": "section",
                "sections": [],
                "text": "Each radiant warden's animating force consists of raw positive energy fused to the soul of a willing sacrifice\u2014usually an astronomer or scholar near the end of their natural life. Focused now on protecting a site from any intrusion\u2014 including by curious archaeologists or adventurers\u2014a radiant warden might pause before an attack if approached peacefully. Unfortunately, these constructs are prone to speaking in vague riddles or complex mathematical diatribes that can be as confusing as they are intriguing; often, discussions break down as frustration mounts on either side (or both).",
                "sources": [
                    {
                        "type": "source",
                        "name": "Bestiary 2",
                        "link": {
                            "type": "link",
                            "name": "Bestiary 2 pg. 220",
